{"tid":2151172,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘋果日報：警方取走資料涉新聞材料　將申請禁制令","createTime":"2020-08-11T09:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T09:56:10.000Z","uid":20933,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1f1615a5137c6c7ab0ac4176f0344b11d7a4f462","tid":2151172,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T09:14:25.000Z","msg":"《蘋果日報》總編輯羅偉光表示，警方昨日在將軍澳大樓搜查行動中取走的「蘋果日報慈善基金」資料涉及新聞材料，《蘋果日報》決定申請臨時禁制令。<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒集團創辦人黎智英昨日被捕後，在旺角警署被通宵扣查，今早10時許，黎智英被押解至西貢遊艇會調查，期間被鎖上手扣，逗留半小時後再被送回旺角警署。下午3時許，黎智英再被押解至西九龍總區警察總部。"},{"pid":"cea6799c77b75db0eccefa7768c54e167099d5b6","tid":2151172,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T09:14:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543103-20200811.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543103-20200811.htm&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FoZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=9e6f1006\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543103-20200811.htm&h=ede36035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543103-20200811.htm</a>"},{"pid":"80da98345a3e489f1351cb82662d50d1c4a34182","tid":2151172,"uid":11008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T09:16:35.000Z","msg":"會唔會有個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4ebe4b8458420cf560055caacea345440724a6","tid":2151172,"uid":158242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T09:17:20.000Z","msg":"琴日又話冇拎走過，今次點解釋"},{"pid":"2ed8951b60fe4a4c40e85eb95d4ed2d791e33ba4","tid":2151172,"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb4ebe4b8458420cf560055caacea345440724a6","tid":2151172,"uid":158242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T09:17:20.000Z","msg":"琴日又話冇拎走過，今次點解釋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T09:21:49.000Z","msg":"李